 not be safe to connect  Connecting to VMI Sentinel VMI Sentinel is limited to Faculty  Staff  and Cadets only  You will need to have an active domain account to be able to logon to this wireless network  For Mac or Android users  simply click to connect to VMI Sentinel wireless network  enter your domain credentials as  vmi username  and click connect  For Windows devices  Use these instructions to connect to VMI Sentinel  and download the Aruba Quick Connect zip file to set your system   This will allow you to access the VMI Sentinel wireless and associated network resources    Wireless Connecting to Wireless Who has access  Wireless Security VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 